readable.content: A brown and white dog with a pink collar is barking at a brown dog with a blue collar in the snow . A dark brown dog is biting at a lighter brown colored dog . The dog with the red collar is bearing its teeth at the dog with the blue collar . Two dogs are on a white carpet with one of the dogs showing its fangs . Two dogs , one with mouth open .
